headline: Equinor Awards North Sea Subsea Contract to SLB OneSubsea
summary: Schlumberger Limited (NYSE:SLB) is one of the best dividend stocks to buy. On August 25, SLB announced that OneSubsea, its joint venture, landed a project contract from Equinor covering design, supply, and construction of a 12-well subsea system in Norway’s Fram Sør field. After a year of early engineering and planning with Equinor, SLB OneSubsea […]
